00:56.240 --> 00:58.242
[♪♪♪]

00:59.040 --> 01:01.646
SELENE: <i>I was an elite soldier
in the vampire army.</i>

01:01.800 --> 01:03.450
<i>A Death Dealer.</i>

01:05.160 --> 01:06.650
<i>And I was good at it.</i>

01:09.240 --> 01:10.685
<i>But I was betrayed.</i>

01:10.880 --> 01:14.646
<i>Viktor, our leader
and the most powerful vampire...</i>

01:14.840 --> 01:17.730
<i>...was not the saviour
he had led me to believe.</i>

01:19.480 --> 01:22.086
<i>Suddenly, allies turned enemies.</i>

01:22.240 --> 01:26.484
<i>The vampire Elders I had once protected
wanted me dead.</i>

01:28.600 --> 01:30.967
<i>Then I found Michael Corvin.</i>

01:31.120 --> 01:35.125
<i>Neither vampire nor Lycan,
Michael became a hybrid.</i>

01:36.520 --> 01:39.649
<i>We retaliated, killed the Elders.</i>

01:41.720 --> 01:44.610
<i>But then everything changed.</i>

01:44.760 --> 01:49.687
<i>I was captured, not knowing that I was
carrying Michael's child.</i>

01:49.880 --> 01:52.850
<i>Eve, our daughter,
the first pure-blood hybrid...</i>

01:53.000 --> 01:55.241
<i>...whose blood could end the war...</i>

01:55.400 --> 01:58.131
<i>...became highly sought after
by both vampires and Lycans alike.</i>

01:58.280 --> 01:59.770
[SCREECHES]

02:02.960 --> 02:07.921
<i>My only choice was to hide her
from the world and from myself...</i>

02:08.080 --> 02:10.241
<i>...so not even I could lead them to her.</i>

02:12.880 --> 02:16.601
[WHISPERING] <i>I was an elite soldier
in the vampire army.</i>

02:20.440 --> 02:24.126
<i>My only choice was to hide her
from the world...</i>

02:24.880 --> 02:28.441
<i>...so not even I could lead them to her.</i>

02:42.640 --> 02:45.883
[IN NORMAL VOICE]
<i>I have lived beyond my time.</i>

02:46.040 --> 02:48.884
<i>Another new moon
in a thousand years of new moons...</i>

02:49.040 --> 02:51.407
[ENGINES REVVING]

02:51.600 --> 02:54.171
<i>...and I do not care to see it.</i>

02:57.880 --> 02:59.041
<i>I have nothing.</i>

02:59.560 --> 03:00.766
<i>My coven...</i>

03:02.080 --> 03:03.809
<i>...my daughter...</i>

03:04.000 --> 03:05.889
<i>- ...my love, all gone.</i>
LYCAN 1: Cut her off!

03:06.560 --> 03:09.086
<i>And soon, perhaps...</i>

03:09.240 --> 03:11.402
<i>...my very existence.</i>

03:11.760 --> 03:13.296
LYCAN 2: Selene's coming!
<i>- I am hunted...</i>

03:13.320 --> 03:15.527
<i>...by vampires and Lycans.</i>

03:16.720 --> 03:20.361
<i>Now I am an outcast, a pariah.</i>

03:22.840 --> 03:24.842
[TYRES SCREECH]

03:28.160 --> 03:29.605
[LYCAN 3 CHUCKLING]

03:29.800 --> 03:33.850
LYCAN 2: Put her down!
LYCAN 1: Remember, he wants her alive.

03:34.000 --> 03:35.047
LYCAN 2:
Fire!

03:35.920 --> 03:36.967
[SELENE GRUNTING]

03:39.080 --> 03:40.650
LYCAN 2:
Come on, now. Fire!

03:42.000 --> 03:43.968
[GRUNTING AND GROANING]

03:47.320 --> 03:48.765
[BREATHING DEEPLY]

03:50.280 --> 03:52.169
[GRUNTING]

04:01.880 --> 04:03.450
[SNARLING]

04:17.600 --> 04:19.442
[GROWLS THEN SNARLING]

04:21.560 --> 04:23.085
[TYRES SCREECHING]

04:23.720 --> 04:25.722
[SQUEALS THEN GUNSHOT]

04:37.240 --> 04:40.005
You are an extremely difficult person
to keep track of.

04:40.160 --> 04:41.525
I don't need you.

04:43.280 --> 04:44.327
But thank you.

04:44.480 --> 04:45.606
Any word with Michael?

04:45.800 --> 04:47.928
- Stop tracking me!
- I'm not tracking you.

04:49.120 --> 04:50.326
I'm looking for Eve.

04:51.280 --> 04:53.965
Well, I'm the very last person
who could help you find my daughter.

04:54.120 --> 04:57.203
Selene, listen to me.
The Lycans are moving again.

04:57.760 --> 04:58.841
No, this is different.

04:59.000 --> 05:01.401
They're organised.
They have a new leader.

05:01.560 --> 05:03.560
- His name is Marius.
- I'm finished with this war.

05:03.600 --> 05:06.126
Well, it's not finished with you.
They could have killed you...

05:06.320 --> 05:08.721
...but clearly their mission
was to capture you.

05:08.880 --> 05:11.724
Your daughter's blood, it's a prize.

05:11.880 --> 05:13.803
And if they find her, if they use it...

05:14.000 --> 05:18.369
- ...Marius's power will be limitless.
- Well, then I hope she remains lost.

05:18.920 --> 05:20.160
[GRUNTS]

05:23.600 --> 05:25.443
I need you to deliver a message.

05:25.600 --> 05:27.728
- Grunt if you understand.
- Unh, unh!

05:27.880 --> 05:29.291
Tell your Marius...

05:29.440 --> 05:31.416
...if he thinks he can extract
information from me...

05:31.440 --> 05:33.169
...to locate my daughter, he can't.

05:33.320 --> 05:35.527
I don't know where she is,
and I don't want to know.

05:35.960 --> 05:37.246
Marius will find you.

05:38.600 --> 05:40.045
[GRUNTING]

05:40.240 --> 05:42.129
Do you understand your message?

05:43.480 --> 05:45.323
[GROANING]

05:52.080 --> 05:53.969
What is it?

05:55.040 --> 05:56.371
Have you seen this before?

05:56.520 --> 05:57.806
SELENE: No...

05:58.000 --> 05:59.490
...but we need to get it out.

05:59.920 --> 06:01.490
[GRUNTING]

06:03.360 --> 06:05.010
Let's go.

06:07.840 --> 06:08.887
[DAVID GROANS]

06:18.320 --> 06:20.322
[♪♪♪]

06:23.840 --> 06:25.416
MALE GUARD 1:
<i>Bravo one, over. Car approaching.</i>

06:25.440 --> 06:27.800
FEMALE GUARD: <i>Access cleared.</i>
MALE GUARD 2: <i>Close the gates.</i>

06:31.280 --> 06:32.880
MALE GUARD 1:
<i>Commencing perimeter sweep.</i>

06:35.720 --> 06:38.405
[♪♪♪]

06:48.040 --> 06:50.486
Privilege to welcome you home at last,
sir.

06:50.680 --> 06:52.762
Semira awaits you
in her private chambers.

06:52.920 --> 06:54.684
Semira?

06:54.840 --> 06:56.285
Where is Cassius?

06:56.440 --> 06:58.256
The entire council will greet you,
of course, sir...

06:58.280 --> 07:01.602
...but Semira requests
just a few moments.

07:01.760 --> 07:03.285
And your name is?

07:03.480 --> 07:04.891
Varga, sir.

07:05.040 --> 07:07.088
I shall try to remember it.

07:16.840 --> 07:18.126
[SNAPS FINGERS]

07:27.840 --> 07:30.571
SEMIRA:... and act accordingly
because of this tragic...

07:30.760 --> 07:32.364
Leave us.

07:35.440 --> 07:39.047
Darling Thomas. It has been...

07:39.200 --> 07:41.601
- ...how long?
- Decades.

07:42.440 --> 07:43.441
Congratulations.

07:43.600 --> 07:45.056
I gather you have a seat
on the council.

07:45.080 --> 07:46.570
I could not be more proud.

07:47.440 --> 07:51.161
It's a shame that your return is not
under more festive circumstances.

07:51.360 --> 07:54.443
It is said that the Western Coven
was utterly destroyed.

07:54.600 --> 07:55.726
Yes, it was.

07:55.880 --> 07:57.848
It's a blessing
you escaped with your life.

07:58.000 --> 08:00.685
Mm. Well, many did not.

08:00.840 --> 08:03.207
There has been too much death
among our people.

08:03.360 --> 08:06.364
These urns are all that remain
of our Budapest Coven.

08:06.520 --> 08:08.488
Well, you have my condolences.

08:08.640 --> 08:11.849
We are losing the war, Thomas.

08:12.000 --> 08:15.288
If we stay as we are, our species
will be extinct within five years.

08:15.440 --> 08:17.044
Does Cassius share your view?

08:17.200 --> 08:19.089
The Lycans have regrouped,
replenished...

08:19.240 --> 08:21.004
...and are resolved
to exterminate us.

08:21.160 --> 08:24.084
Oh, surely, you're safe here.
The Eastern Coven is a fortress.

08:24.240 --> 08:26.402
We are no longer
the coven you remember.

08:26.560 --> 08:28.767
We have fewer Death Dealers
than ever before.

08:28.920 --> 08:31.161
You seem to be surrounded
by new cadets.

08:31.360 --> 08:34.568
Raw recruits, neither combat-ready
nor numerous enough...

08:34.760 --> 08:36.649
...to repel a large-scale Lycan attack.

08:37.600 --> 08:40.683
There has never been
a large-scale Lycan attack.

08:41.520 --> 08:43.409
At least not a coordinated one.

08:43.559 --> 08:46.245
There has never been a Marius.

08:47.040 --> 08:50.601
Pains me to admit it,
but for the first time in my life...

08:51.040 --> 08:53.281
...I genuinely fear for our future.

08:54.040 --> 08:56.281
So, what is your plan?

08:57.960 --> 09:00.645
Semira, you always have a plan.

09:00.800 --> 09:04.361
This little mise-en-scene
you're performing has a purpose.

09:04.560 --> 09:05.846
I am not a mind reader.

09:06.000 --> 09:07.843
Kindly do an old vampire
the courtesy...

09:08.000 --> 09:11.402
...of telling him why
he's been invited here.

09:15.320 --> 09:17.084
Selene.

09:17.280 --> 09:19.044
DAVID:
Come on. We need to keep moving.

09:19.240 --> 09:21.288
SELENE: There are safe houses
far closer than this.

09:21.440 --> 09:23.329
DAVID:
I told you, they destroyed them.

09:23.480 --> 09:25.244
It's different now. Come on.

09:25.520 --> 09:27.522
[♪♪♪]

09:27.720 --> 09:29.563
THOMAS:
But you signed her death warrant.

09:29.720 --> 09:31.848
SEMIRA:
Of course. I despise her.

09:32.000 --> 09:33.684
She killed Viktor. I was his regent.

09:33.880 --> 09:36.406
Until he met Selene.

09:36.560 --> 09:38.688
So you want her to hunt Marius?

09:38.840 --> 09:40.444
I want her to train our new recruits...

09:40.640 --> 09:43.450
...so we have 100 Death Dealers
hunting Marius.

09:43.640 --> 09:48.009
Heh, heh. I doubt she will agree.
Her only concern is for her daughter.

09:48.160 --> 09:49.400
Eve, the hybrid.

09:49.560 --> 09:52.484
Unfortunately, the poor girl
is half Lycan.

09:53.000 --> 09:55.016
It's a vampire's instinct
to condescend to Lycans...

09:55.040 --> 09:56.724
...but they're not afraid to evolve.

09:56.880 --> 09:59.486
Meanwhile,
we stagnate from 1500 years...

09:59.640 --> 10:02.803
...of this damned "species purity"
nonsense.

10:02.960 --> 10:04.928
Huh. And the irony is that Selene...

10:05.120 --> 10:07.885
- ...is probably the purest of us all.
- So the rumour's true?

10:08.320 --> 10:10.448
Her blood has elements
of the Corvinus strain?

10:10.600 --> 10:12.489
She is special.

10:14.040 --> 10:15.963
She brought my son back
from the dead.

10:17.480 --> 10:20.290
- Her blood restarted his heart.
- Impossible.

10:21.360 --> 10:25.445
I witnessed it myself.
She saved my son's life.

10:27.000 --> 10:29.651
Viktor and Amelia.

10:30.080 --> 10:33.129
Side by side for eternity.

10:35.840 --> 10:38.969
You were very fond of Amelia,
if I remember.

10:40.720 --> 10:44.725
- I need you to be my ally on this.
- She won't risk coming here...

10:44.880 --> 10:47.531
...unless she gets an invitation
from the whole council.

10:47.680 --> 10:49.762
And I could never solicit
such a request.

10:49.960 --> 10:51.928
Cassius is protective of the old ways.

10:52.080 --> 10:55.243
He barely tolerates my seat
on the council as it is.

10:55.680 --> 10:58.524
But these are desperate times, Thomas.

10:58.720 --> 11:02.247
And that is why you
must convince the council to invite her.

11:02.400 --> 11:03.526
Ahh...

11:03.960 --> 11:05.325
They arrive tonight.

11:05.480 --> 11:08.689
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Dawn alert. Sixty seconds to sunrise.</i>

11:11.120 --> 11:13.122
[♪♪♪]

11:15.920 --> 11:17.922
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING IN DISTANCE]

11:38.080 --> 11:39.923
Marius, the pack leaders have arrived...

11:40.080 --> 11:42.481
...and I told them to wait
for you in the war room.

11:42.680 --> 11:44.120
MARIUS:
Fighting like dogs, no doubt.

11:44.200 --> 11:46.726
- I'll handle it. Thank you.
- All right.

11:48.040 --> 11:50.042
[INDISTINCT ARGUING]

11:51.120 --> 11:52.840
LYCAN 1: Go on, then.
LYCAN 2: Right, right.

11:52.960 --> 11:54.200
Come around, come around.

11:54.400 --> 11:55.731
LYCAN 1:
No! Listen to me.

11:55.880 --> 11:57.928
We're gonna wedge them in.
That's what we do.

11:58.080 --> 11:59.976
From this side and that side,
we just wedge them in...

12:00.000 --> 12:01.696
...and squeeze them out.
LYCAN 3: Wedge them in?

12:01.720 --> 12:04.485
Is that your plan?
It's not gonna lead to anything.

12:04.640 --> 12:06.440
LYCAN 4: He's getting angry.
LYCAN 3: Shut up!

12:06.520 --> 12:07.567
Stop!

12:07.720 --> 12:09.484
[GROWLS]

12:12.480 --> 12:14.482
- Are you a slave?
- No.

12:14.640 --> 12:16.244
Then don't behave like one.

12:18.000 --> 12:19.650
Look at this map.

12:19.840 --> 12:21.444
What do you see?

12:21.600 --> 12:23.489
Do you see Lycans
fighting over scraps?

12:25.240 --> 12:27.004
I'll tell you what I see.

12:27.640 --> 12:28.926
Volhynia.

12:29.440 --> 12:32.046
Nordgau. Thuringia.

12:32.200 --> 12:33.281
The Lycan victories.

12:35.240 --> 12:36.651
I see vampires dead.

12:36.800 --> 12:38.370
I see entire regions annihilated.

12:38.520 --> 12:40.887
But we will get no further
if we fight amongst ourselves.

12:41.720 --> 12:43.245
We must not rest...

12:43.400 --> 12:46.768
...until we have destroyed
their final sanctuary.

12:47.360 --> 12:50.250
Together, we are strong.

12:51.040 --> 12:54.681
And when we have the blood
of the hybrid girl...

12:56.520 --> 12:58.648
...we will be invincible.

13:06.560 --> 13:07.641
Gregor.

13:07.800 --> 13:09.006
[GREGOR GRUNTS]

13:09.920 --> 13:11.570
You have returned alone.

13:12.920 --> 13:15.127
- We were taken by surprise.
- Where is Selene?

13:15.800 --> 13:18.007
- She spared me.
- Why?

13:18.160 --> 13:19.605
To deliver a message.

13:21.040 --> 13:23.725
She wants you to know
that her daughter is gone forever...

13:23.880 --> 13:25.450
...that you can never find her...

13:25.600 --> 13:28.444
...because even Selene
doesn't know where she's been hidden.

13:28.720 --> 13:29.721
Do you believe her?

13:34.200 --> 13:35.440
Do you believe her?

13:35.760 --> 13:37.967
[PANTING]

13:42.200 --> 13:44.851
I put a tracer in her companion.

13:46.360 --> 13:47.885
Well...

13:49.080 --> 13:51.970
...that means you're not
completely incompetent.

13:58.800 --> 13:59.847
[CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

14:00.040 --> 14:01.451
[DEVICE BEEPS]

14:04.960 --> 14:06.291
[GRUNTS]

14:06.440 --> 14:07.680
Try and stay still.

14:07.840 --> 14:09.285
[DEVICE BEEPS]

14:11.560 --> 14:14.211
- What is it?
- It's some sort of bullet.

14:14.360 --> 14:17.125
It's burrowing through you
faster than you can heal.

14:17.280 --> 14:18.566
It's self-propelled.

14:18.720 --> 14:22.167
That's what I was trying to tell you.
These Lycans are sophisticated.

14:25.200 --> 14:27.282
I don't know if I can remove it in time.

14:27.440 --> 14:29.721
Well, the least you can do
is attempt to sound reassuring.

14:30.160 --> 14:31.889
I'm going to attempt not to kill you.

14:33.000 --> 14:34.843
That will have to do.

14:38.160 --> 14:39.730
[DAVID GRUNTS]

14:42.280 --> 14:43.486
[GRUNTS]

14:53.280 --> 14:54.566
[GROANS]

14:59.960 --> 15:01.962
[WHIRRING]

15:09.120 --> 15:12.920
CASSIUS: To whom do you want us
to offer safe haven and amnesty?

15:13.080 --> 15:16.687
- To Selene the Death Dealer.
- The same Selene who murdered Viktor?

15:16.840 --> 15:18.800
I need no reminder, Cassius,
of what she has done.

15:18.920 --> 15:20.081
Shame on you, sir.

15:20.240 --> 15:23.130
I will not hear her name spoken again.

15:23.320 --> 15:25.448
Cassius, I share your outrage.

15:26.240 --> 15:28.368
Whatever has possessed you?

15:28.520 --> 15:30.045
THOMAS:
If we don't act decisively...

15:30.240 --> 15:32.240
...the war will be at your gate
within a fortnight.

15:32.720 --> 15:35.166
And that is precisely
where it will remain.

15:35.320 --> 15:38.483
No Lycan pack would dare
to attack our coven.

15:38.640 --> 15:40.768
Our defences would rip them apart.

15:40.960 --> 15:43.201
THOMAS:
An ordinary Lycan pack, perhaps...

15:43.360 --> 15:46.523
...but Marius has gathered a force
far more powerful than any...

15:46.680 --> 15:48.011
Unsubstantiated hyperbole.

15:48.160 --> 15:50.003
You need Selene.

15:50.160 --> 15:54.802
Her prowess, her leadership,
her intimate knowledge of Lycans.

15:54.960 --> 15:57.486
And her combat skills
are second to none.

15:57.680 --> 16:00.160
He's right, she is the most lethal
Death Dealer we've ever had.

16:00.360 --> 16:03.887
But she killed one of her own.

16:04.040 --> 16:08.090
Not only the most powerful
and respected of the Elders...

16:08.240 --> 16:12.689
...her protector, who loved her
like his own daughter.

16:12.840 --> 16:14.729
She cannot be trusted.

16:14.880 --> 16:16.166
She has been judged.

16:16.320 --> 16:18.891
Perhaps she can also be redeemed.

16:19.080 --> 16:21.560
It pains me to say it,
but Thomas is right.

16:22.040 --> 16:24.691
No warrior has proved herself
more in battle.

16:24.840 --> 16:28.128
She would be invaluable
in our fight against Marius...

16:28.280 --> 16:32.330
...perhaps even the pivotal element
to secure our victory.

16:34.800 --> 16:36.882
If she can be found...

16:37.040 --> 16:41.568
...and sets foot
within this precious coven...

16:41.840 --> 16:44.889
...I will hold you, Semira,
personally responsible...

16:45.040 --> 16:46.804
- ...for controlling her.
- Of course.

16:58.240 --> 16:59.651
[GASPS]

17:11.200 --> 17:15.444
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Intruder. Intruder. Intruder.</i>

17:15.599 --> 17:17.489
<i>Intruder. Intruder.</i>

17:18.200 --> 17:20.202
[♪♪♪]

17:30.000 --> 17:31.445
[GRUNTING]

17:31.880 --> 17:33.530
Who sent you?

17:34.920 --> 17:36.604
Drop it.

17:42.080 --> 17:43.411
How'd you find us?

17:43.720 --> 17:45.802
There are only a handful
of safe houses left.

17:46.560 --> 17:48.927
The Lycans made it rather easy.

17:49.080 --> 17:51.481
The council of the Eastern Coven
sent me to bring you in.

17:51.640 --> 17:53.369
- For trial?
- No.

17:53.520 --> 17:57.491
- For your safety, and ours.
- You cannot expect me to believe that.

17:57.680 --> 17:59.921
Every single one of them
signed my death warrant.

18:00.080 --> 18:02.208
- Times change.
- Vampires do not.

18:02.680 --> 18:03.920
This is from your father.

18:06.280 --> 18:08.328
Is it authentic?

18:08.520 --> 18:10.568
It's his seal, his handwriting.

18:10.720 --> 18:13.929
The council has offered you clemency
and granted us both safe haven.

18:14.080 --> 18:15.889
- Why?
- Marius.

18:16.040 --> 18:18.441
It is the council's humble request...

18:18.600 --> 18:21.285
...that you train us
to defeat him and his army.

18:22.920 --> 18:24.126
LYCAN:
Move. Come on.

18:24.280 --> 18:25.930
The signal's coming from this way.

18:27.200 --> 18:29.009
Look, I understand you're reluctant...

18:29.160 --> 18:32.004
...but as guests of the council,
we will be protected by law.

18:32.160 --> 18:34.322
My father wouldn't lie,
and he holds no grudge.

18:34.480 --> 18:35.840
He had no love for Viktor, either.

18:35.960 --> 18:37.450
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Intruder. Intruder.</i>

18:37.600 --> 18:39.762
- Lycans.
<i>- Intruder.</i>

18:42.120 --> 18:44.930
- We must leave.
- You should accept the council's offer.

18:45.080 --> 18:47.003
- For Eve.
- Eve does not want my help.

18:47.160 --> 18:49.527
I know you want to protect her.
And if we destroy Marius...

18:49.680 --> 18:51.842
...we destroy the greatest threat
to her safety.

18:52.000 --> 18:53.286
Now.

18:58.160 --> 18:59.525
[♪♪♪]

19:10.120 --> 19:11.451
Marius.

19:14.640 --> 19:16.165
We just missed them.

19:16.320 --> 19:19.881
I do not wish to hear
the word "just" again.

19:20.400 --> 19:22.641
Either we have her or we have nothing.

19:24.120 --> 19:25.849
Do you understand?

19:26.000 --> 19:28.082
- Do you understand?
- Yeah.

19:33.080 --> 19:35.162
[INDISTINCT ANNOUNCEMENT
OVER PA]

19:37.600 --> 19:39.648
[TRAIN WHISTLE BLOWS]

19:45.840 --> 19:47.604
GUARD 1:
<i>Tango Charlie approaching.</i>

19:47.760 --> 19:49.171
GUARD 2:
<i>All clear.</i>

19:50.600 --> 19:52.329
<i>Perimeter secure.</i>

20:06.200 --> 20:07.850
- Welcome.
- Am I?

20:08.000 --> 20:10.571
Our coven's resources
and weaponry are yours...

20:10.720 --> 20:14.281
...to transform these raw recruits
into Death Dealers worthy of your name.

20:14.480 --> 20:16.608
Varga will be your right-hand man.

20:16.760 --> 20:18.489
He knows all our strengths
and weaknesses.

20:18.640 --> 20:22.247
He is also our most prolific Lycan killer,
with over 40 confirmed kills.

20:22.400 --> 20:24.323
- It's an honour.
SEMIRA: David, welcome.

20:24.480 --> 20:27.211
- Thank you.
- To mark the safe arrival of our guests...

20:27.360 --> 20:29.522
...I've arranged a little soiree
in the Winter Garden.

20:29.880 --> 20:31.530
There's really no need. Thank you.

20:31.680 --> 20:34.445
Nonsense. There's always a need
to indulge in pleasure.

20:40.280 --> 20:42.521
[MUSICIANS PLAYING
CLASSICAL MUSIC]

20:56.120 --> 20:57.804
[MUSIC STOPS]

20:57.960 --> 20:59.689
In times of war...

20:59.840 --> 21:02.684
...this coven needs moments
to celebrate.

21:02.920 --> 21:06.811
The arrival of Thomas,
David and Selene...

21:06.960 --> 21:09.930
...is reason aplenty to rejoice.

21:11.240 --> 21:13.288
To us all.

21:14.160 --> 21:17.323
[THUNDER RUMBLING
AND CRASHING]

21:18.400 --> 21:20.402
[MUSICIANS CONTINUE PLAYING]

21:26.240 --> 21:28.527
It's good of you to offer us
sanctuary, Semira. Thank you.

21:28.720 --> 21:31.166
It will be entirely my pleasure.

21:31.360 --> 21:35.081
Tell me, is it true that her blood
brought you back to life?

21:35.240 --> 21:36.651
Yes, it is.

21:36.800 --> 21:38.564
I owe her everything.

21:39.600 --> 21:43.127
But, if you'll excuse me,
my father requests my counsel.

21:45.520 --> 21:47.124
Thomas was always such a bore.

21:51.200 --> 21:54.283
THOMAS: Well, Semira's certainly
taken an interest in you.

21:54.440 --> 21:57.205
Well, the interest is certainly
not mutual.

21:57.360 --> 21:59.647
We need her protection.

21:59.800 --> 22:02.451
On the contrary,
I think I need protection from her.

22:02.600 --> 22:04.284
THOMAS:
The Battle of the Peste.

22:05.040 --> 22:07.361
We thought it would be
the one to end the war...

22:07.520 --> 22:08.931
...the final conflict...

22:09.080 --> 22:10.923
...but here we are still.

22:11.080 --> 22:14.766
I hope you see my bid for clemency
for Selene for what it is.

22:14.920 --> 22:16.684
Clemency
is the least you can offer her...

22:16.840 --> 22:18.336
...after bartering her daughter
to the Lycans.

22:18.360 --> 22:22.001
I lost so much during this war.

22:22.160 --> 22:25.528
Believe me, I am haunted still
by all those I failed.

22:25.680 --> 22:28.251
Well, then you must help me
protect her.

22:28.400 --> 22:30.402
She has lost even more
than we can imagine.

22:30.560 --> 22:32.608
And she's important to me.

22:35.680 --> 22:38.206
[THUNDER CONTINUES
CRASHING AND RUMBLING]

22:43.880 --> 22:46.201
Marius is out there...

22:46.360 --> 22:50.524
...reeking of canine insolence,
plotting our downfall.

22:53.240 --> 22:57.211
We do not need Selene to destroy him.

22:58.160 --> 22:59.764
I am more than capable.

22:59.920 --> 23:02.446
No, Varga, you are merely adequate.

23:02.600 --> 23:06.127
It's fortunate that we're not forced
to rely on your skills for our survival.

23:06.560 --> 23:09.643
That, my sweet...

23:09.920 --> 23:12.241
...yet unimaginative bedfellow...

23:12.400 --> 23:13.765
...is my area of expertise.

23:13.920 --> 23:15.684
- I think you should...
- Don't think, Varga.

23:15.840 --> 23:17.604
You'll hurt yourself.

23:18.360 --> 23:22.410
There are other ways
to prove your devotion.

23:33.680 --> 23:38.129
Piece by delicate piece...

23:39.360 --> 23:40.407
[SEMIRA MOANS]

23:41.320 --> 23:44.005
...the puzzle will fall into place.

23:46.160 --> 23:47.969
Oh, yeah...

23:49.280 --> 23:50.930
Yeah...

23:52.760 --> 23:53.807
[GASPS]

23:56.200 --> 23:58.202
[♪♪♪]

24:17.000 --> 24:18.604
[GRUNTS]

24:24.520 --> 24:25.806
[GASPS]

24:28.880 --> 24:31.121
Don't aim where the Lycan is.
Anticipate.

24:37.360 --> 24:39.647
And remember,
a Lycan is never more vulnerable...

24:39.800 --> 24:41.040
...than when he's in wolf form.

24:41.200 --> 24:42.770
- What?
- That makes no sense.

24:42.960 --> 24:44.450
[ALL MURMURING]

24:44.600 --> 24:46.160
In wolf form,
they cannot use weapons...

24:46.280 --> 24:48.647
...and their thinking
becomes much more primitive...

24:48.840 --> 24:50.046
...driven only by bloodlust.

24:50.200 --> 24:52.965
- How many have you killed?
- I don't keep track.

24:53.440 --> 24:56.250
I'm increasing Lycan speed
by 20 percent.

24:58.600 --> 25:00.409
Please continue.

25:05.640 --> 25:08.450
My pack's probed the Eastern Coven's
perimeter for weaknesses...

25:08.600 --> 25:09.601
...and there are none.

25:09.760 --> 25:11.800
And any direct assault
would trigger the lockdown...

25:11.920 --> 25:13.400
...which makes the coven impregnable.

25:13.480 --> 25:16.290
Even if we could break inside
without losing 90 percent of our force...

25:16.440 --> 25:18.016
- ...they have fallback positions...
- This.

25:18.040 --> 25:20.805
- ...that can be...
- Is this ready?

25:20.960 --> 25:22.644
Yeah.

25:22.800 --> 25:25.280
When we have the hybrid's blood...

25:25.440 --> 25:27.204
...we launch against the Eastern.

25:27.360 --> 25:29.647
Find Selene, and we find her daughter.

25:29.840 --> 25:31.444
[BOTH GRUNTING]

25:34.520 --> 25:36.443
My own invention.

25:36.600 --> 25:38.416
One of the first things
a Death Dealer must learn...

25:38.440 --> 25:39.976
...is how to fight in a confined space.

25:40.000 --> 25:41.126
Of course, the one thing...

25:41.280 --> 25:43.521
...this training session lacks
is unpredictability.

25:44.800 --> 25:47.007
Perhaps you'll indulge me
and give my students...

25:47.160 --> 25:51.722
Uh, I should say your students.
--a lesson in combat's unpredictability.

25:51.880 --> 25:55.771
It would not only honour us, but it
would be invaluable to their training.

25:55.920 --> 25:57.763
- I don't...
- Please.

25:59.520 --> 26:01.010
That's enough.

26:02.080 --> 26:05.243
Gather round.
We are going to school you...

26:05.400 --> 26:08.449
...in the true nature
of the Lycan warrior.

26:08.600 --> 26:12.650
For the sake of this lesson,
our esteemed guest Selene...

26:12.840 --> 26:16.208
...will play the role of Death Dealer
bravely defending our fortress...

26:16.360 --> 26:19.967
...and I will take the role
of Lycan villain...

26:20.120 --> 26:21.690
...here to destroy it.

26:21.840 --> 26:23.330
Ladies first.

26:23.560 --> 26:25.562
[♪♪♪]

26:41.400 --> 26:42.970
[BOTH GRUNTING]

26:43.600 --> 26:44.761
[VARGA CHUCKLES]

26:46.200 --> 26:47.281
Impressive.

26:55.200 --> 26:56.565
Come on.

26:59.680 --> 27:00.806
Come on.

27:20.440 --> 27:21.521
[GROANS]

27:32.800 --> 27:34.165
[SELENE GRUNTS]

27:34.640 --> 27:35.687
[SELENE GASPS]

27:38.000 --> 27:40.048
[SELENE PANTING]

27:40.840 --> 27:42.365
Tonight's lesson:

27:42.520 --> 27:45.922
Do not trust your opponent
to fight with honour.

27:46.080 --> 27:48.128
They are Lycan. They have none.

27:49.200 --> 27:50.531
Ah!

27:52.480 --> 27:53.686
Don't move.

27:56.200 --> 27:57.725
[GASPING]

28:01.880 --> 28:03.803
Nightshade.

28:03.960 --> 28:06.406
Leeches into vampire cells,
usually fatal.

28:06.560 --> 28:09.803
But for one with her strength,
there will only be pain...

28:10.000 --> 28:11.206
...followed by paralysis.

28:11.360 --> 28:12.930
I'll kill you.

28:14.200 --> 28:16.248
UV bullets.

28:22.080 --> 28:25.368
Did you honestly think
I would forgive you for killing Viktor?

28:25.520 --> 28:27.409
Varga, you have orders.

28:28.040 --> 28:29.565
[GASPING]

28:29.760 --> 28:31.205
Varga!

28:54.960 --> 28:56.962
[SCREAMING]

29:02.000 --> 29:04.002
I don't need you to train Death Dealers.

29:04.160 --> 29:06.083
I have Varga for that.

29:06.240 --> 29:08.925
All that I need to rule this coven...

29:09.080 --> 29:13.847
...and end the march of the Lycans
is your blood.

29:21.040 --> 29:22.371
What about the bodies?

29:24.760 --> 29:26.205
Sound the alarm.

29:26.720 --> 29:28.961
Have the council find them.

29:29.160 --> 29:34.405
Conclusive evidence of the atrocity
committed by Selene.

29:34.960 --> 29:36.450
[MOANS SOFTLY]

29:37.320 --> 29:39.322
[GASPING]

29:40.640 --> 29:42.642
[ALARM WAILING]

29:43.800 --> 29:45.040
There's been a breach.

29:45.760 --> 29:46.807
We need to find Selene.

29:46.960 --> 29:50.407
- Cordoned off. Semira's orders.
- Step aside.

29:53.880 --> 29:55.120
David.

29:56.360 --> 29:57.566
Come.

29:58.000 --> 30:01.243
There's more than one way
to move around this coven.

30:01.440 --> 30:04.330
Amelia created these passageways
centuries ago.

30:08.400 --> 30:09.447
Where does this lead?

30:09.600 --> 30:13.241
To the private chambers,
including Semira's.

30:24.040 --> 30:26.042
[♪♪♪]

30:39.080 --> 30:40.764
What the hell have they done to her?

30:40.920 --> 30:44.049
<i>Machina sanguinem exhauri.</i>

30:44.200 --> 30:46.726
Bloodletting.

30:49.200 --> 30:53.364
Semira wants Selene's
most precious asset.

30:54.280 --> 30:56.442
- This is gonna kill her.
- Eventually, yes...

30:56.600 --> 30:59.285
...but it will be agonisingly slow.

31:04.240 --> 31:05.810
Look.

31:05.960 --> 31:09.442
This is designed to open the arteries
as wide as possible.

31:09.600 --> 31:12.922
If we're not very careful,
we will do her more harm than good.

31:13.440 --> 31:14.771
Careful.

31:17.240 --> 31:19.242
[♪♪♪]

31:33.280 --> 31:35.169
CASSIUS:
Is this hers?

31:35.320 --> 31:36.321
SEMIRA:
Yes.

31:36.480 --> 31:39.086
Selene uses only
this particular weapon.

31:41.000 --> 31:42.809
A known traitor within our walls.

31:43.000 --> 31:44.604
This is precisely what I foresaw...

31:44.760 --> 31:48.082
...and what you assured me
you would prevent.

31:48.360 --> 31:50.169
Their blood is upon your hands.

31:50.320 --> 31:52.368
- Sir, I did everything...
- Do not speak to me.

31:52.520 --> 31:53.760
There can be no mercy.

31:53.920 --> 31:56.491
I want her hunted
to the ends of the Earth.

31:56.680 --> 31:58.569
It shall be done.

32:00.120 --> 32:01.963
CASSIUS:
And I want her captured alive.

32:04.720 --> 32:06.848
Is that understood?

32:07.000 --> 32:08.923
Perfectly.

32:11.640 --> 32:14.644
[♪♪♪]

32:18.200 --> 32:20.646
- We're running out of time.
THOMAS: All right, take her.

32:20.800 --> 32:22.768
You must go north, far north.

32:23.000 --> 32:24.445
Var Dohr.

32:26.400 --> 32:27.606
No.

32:27.760 --> 32:29.762
Father and son united in treason.

32:29.920 --> 32:31.604
Carry on with Selene.

32:32.760 --> 32:33.761
I'll deal with them.

32:33.920 --> 32:35.160
Oh...

32:35.320 --> 32:36.924
[♪♪♪]

32:39.960 --> 32:41.610
[ALL GRUNTING]

32:43.160 --> 32:44.161
DAVID:
Come on.

32:55.560 --> 32:56.846
Go! Now!

32:57.640 --> 32:59.165
DAVID:
No!

33:00.640 --> 33:02.802
[GRUNTS THEN GROANS]

33:08.360 --> 33:11.409
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Dawn alert. Sixty seconds to sunrise.</i>

33:11.560 --> 33:14.291
Go ahead. The sun will burn you
to ashes out there...

33:14.440 --> 33:16.442
...or you can die
with some grace in here.

33:20.800 --> 33:22.086
[YELLS]

33:42.960 --> 33:44.041
[DAVID GRUNTS]

33:46.120 --> 33:47.565
They can walk in the sun.

34:06.040 --> 34:08.565
You need to feed.
You've lost too much blood.

34:18.320 --> 34:19.650
[BOTH GRUNTING]

34:26.639 --> 34:29.405
THOMAS: That child... Because he
helped that child of yours.

34:29.560 --> 34:32.005
My son is dead. Dead.

34:32.199 --> 34:33.246
David.

34:34.360 --> 34:35.360
Take her now.

34:35.520 --> 34:37.170
You must go north. Var Dohr.

34:39.880 --> 34:41.530
Go! Now!

34:41.719 --> 34:43.005
[GRUNTS THEN GROANS]

34:49.080 --> 34:50.809
[BOTH PANTING]

34:54.120 --> 34:55.849
Thank you.

34:59.560 --> 35:03.451
I'm very sorry
that you lost your father.

35:03.760 --> 35:06.411
He put up a valiant fight.

35:06.880 --> 35:10.168
It's strange to lose someone
you feel like you never really knew.

35:12.160 --> 35:14.242
I feel the same about my mother, but...

35:15.440 --> 35:17.488
I have almost no memory of her.

35:18.560 --> 35:20.244
And I of Eve.

35:21.520 --> 35:23.329
I didn't want her.

35:23.840 --> 35:25.330
I didn't know her.

35:26.240 --> 35:27.241
And now I've lost her.

35:27.400 --> 35:29.687
Why do you insist on saying
that you've lost her?

35:30.200 --> 35:33.761
She made me promise
I would never look for her...

35:33.920 --> 35:36.651
...that I would never consider myself
having a daughter.

35:37.440 --> 35:38.646
And she was right.

35:40.520 --> 35:42.966
Nothing good has come
to anyone I love.

35:43.480 --> 35:46.882
You're family,
and you're all I have left.

35:49.440 --> 35:51.329
Well, then, you really are in trouble.

35:53.280 --> 35:55.248
You need to rest.

36:01.440 --> 36:03.442
[♪♪♪]

36:04.120 --> 36:06.248
SEMIRA: Selene's clearly
in league with the Lycans.

36:06.720 --> 36:09.530
Thomas and David were complicit
in this treachery.

36:09.680 --> 36:13.082
They walked in the sun. This alone
is evidence of Lycan collusion.

36:13.240 --> 36:16.210
Selene must be wiped from the pages
of our proud history.

36:16.400 --> 36:17.447
SEMIRA:
Alexia.

36:17.600 --> 36:20.524
- We shall avenge our fallen.
- See to it that you do.

36:26.880 --> 36:29.326
[♪♪♪]

36:46.680 --> 36:50.765
- How much nightshade did you use?
- I thought it best to err on the side...

36:50.960 --> 36:53.327
Varga, what have we said
about you thinking?

36:53.920 --> 36:55.524
The poison will dissipate.

36:55.680 --> 36:58.968
I need this blood untainted,
and I need it now.

36:59.120 --> 37:01.282
It cannot be rushed.

37:01.800 --> 37:03.131
It must run its course.

37:07.520 --> 37:12.845
It's definitely the car.
But no sign of where they went.

37:13.480 --> 37:15.084
Spread out across the city.

37:15.240 --> 37:16.810
Search everywhere.

37:17.440 --> 37:19.442
[TRAIN WHISTLE BLOWING]

37:19.600 --> 37:22.444
[MAN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY
OVER PA]

37:23.880 --> 37:27.487
MAN [OVER PA]: <i>The train at
platform four terminates at this station.</i>

37:41.840 --> 37:43.285
[TRAIN WHISTLE BLOWS]

37:44.360 --> 37:45.885
Northbound.

37:46.040 --> 37:48.884
[♪♪♪]

38:00.360 --> 38:03.204
I will be more powerful...

38:04.400 --> 38:06.368
...than Cassius...

38:08.680 --> 38:10.728
...than any vampire in this coven.

38:10.880 --> 38:13.281
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

38:18.800 --> 38:21.320
- What news of the search?
- Selene and David are heading north.

38:21.440 --> 38:23.761
- Of course they are.
- Your Grace?

38:23.920 --> 38:25.922
They will run to the only
remaining coven...

38:26.080 --> 38:29.323
...to afford them safe haven:
Var Dohr, the Nordic fortress.

38:29.480 --> 38:31.244
But Var Dohr is only a legend.

38:31.400 --> 38:33.926
I would not give it
such an elevated status.

38:34.120 --> 38:38.523
It is a frigid, dreary outpost
full of pathetic, peace-loving cowards.

38:38.680 --> 38:41.081
You speak of it
as if you have actually been there.

38:41.240 --> 38:45.529
Where do you think I was
when Viktor wasted years with Selene?

38:46.800 --> 38:48.404
Prepare yourself.

38:48.560 --> 38:51.370
The journey's long,
and I need you to take it alone.

38:52.360 --> 38:54.681
I must be certain the traitor's there...

38:54.840 --> 38:58.765
...before I risk sending a full squad
of Death Dealers so far from this coven.

39:06.160 --> 39:08.162
[♪♪♪]

39:15.520 --> 39:17.409
[ALL CLAMOURING]

39:17.560 --> 39:18.607
[BOTH GROWLING]

39:29.560 --> 39:30.846
[ALEXIA GASPS]

39:31.040 --> 39:32.644
You need to be more careful.

39:41.360 --> 39:42.930
You need to be more gentle.

39:47.560 --> 39:49.130
- Have you found Selene?
- Yes.

39:49.320 --> 39:51.368
She is headed for the Nordic Coven.

39:53.840 --> 39:56.491
I risk everything for this.

39:56.640 --> 40:00.611
- For you, for us.
- I know, my love.

40:00.760 --> 40:04.082
Semira grows more insane
for power with each day.

40:04.240 --> 40:05.890
She must be stopped.

40:06.040 --> 40:09.044
And every day, I fear more
what she will do if we are discovered.

40:10.520 --> 40:14.684
I cannot attack the Eastern Coven
without the blood of the hybrid.

40:14.840 --> 40:17.730
It's too strong, even for my horde.

40:18.840 --> 40:20.490
Selene...

40:21.160 --> 40:25.370
She is the key to the futures
of Lycans and vampires alike.

40:25.800 --> 40:27.768
You shall have her.

40:34.160 --> 40:36.162
[♪♪♪]

40:55.120 --> 40:57.327
SELENE:
Var Dohr is just beyond that ridge.

40:57.520 --> 40:59.568
[WIND WHISTLING]

41:14.000 --> 41:16.571
[♪♪♪]

41:21.440 --> 41:23.442
[HORSES SNORTING]

41:32.440 --> 41:34.442
[WIND WHISTLING]

42:49.440 --> 42:51.442
[♪♪♪]

42:58.280 --> 43:00.169
Where is everyone?

43:00.960 --> 43:02.644
Watching.

43:10.120 --> 43:12.646
We come seeking sanctuary...

43:12.800 --> 43:14.450
...not to fight.

43:15.840 --> 43:17.888
Then you've come to the right place.

43:22.920 --> 43:24.729
My name is Lena.

43:24.880 --> 43:26.723
Follow me.

43:28.000 --> 43:29.650
What was that?

43:29.800 --> 43:31.723
Some kind of trick.

43:35.160 --> 43:37.367
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING]

43:44.600 --> 43:46.489
[SPEAKING IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

43:58.880 --> 44:00.405
VIDAR:
You must be Selene.

44:00.960 --> 44:03.406
Does the great Death Dealer
truly come in peace?

44:04.000 --> 44:06.002
- I do.
- And what about this one?

44:06.200 --> 44:08.407
SELENE:
This is David, son of Thomas.

44:08.560 --> 44:12.087
Who I haven't seen
for many, many years.

44:14.960 --> 44:16.769
VIDAR:
You must excuse the attention.

44:16.960 --> 44:20.328
Our coven doesn't receive
many guests, by design.

44:20.480 --> 44:21.481
We do as we wish...

44:21.640 --> 44:24.246
- ...not as others would have us do.
- And what of the Lycans?

44:24.400 --> 44:26.767
VIDAR: We are too far removed
for them to take notice...

44:26.920 --> 44:31.130
...and even if they did, our climate
is quite an obstacle to warm-bloods.

44:31.600 --> 44:33.648
This coven wouldn't exist...

44:33.800 --> 44:36.406
- ...without your mother's grace.
- You knew my mother?

44:36.560 --> 44:38.164
All vampires do, my boy.

44:38.360 --> 44:40.681
No. My mother was low-born.
She died giving birth to me.

44:40.840 --> 44:44.208
A falsehood, you will find, designed
to keep your true lineage safe.

44:44.360 --> 44:45.805
- Is she still alive?
- No.

44:46.360 --> 44:49.330
And her death
was a terrible blow to our kind.

44:49.480 --> 44:52.165
The mourning ceremony we held
lasted for an entire month.

44:52.320 --> 44:55.051
Such an honour
is usually reserved for a high-born...

44:55.200 --> 44:56.804
- ...a Grand Elder.
- Yes.

44:59.280 --> 45:01.044
- Amelia.
- Yes.

45:01.200 --> 45:03.726
How could a Grand Elder
have been my mother...

45:03.880 --> 45:05.086
...and I not been told?

45:05.760 --> 45:07.603
I have something for you.

45:15.080 --> 45:17.082
[♪♪♪]

45:23.320 --> 45:26.881
Your father's greatest work,
infused with silver.

45:27.040 --> 45:29.646
The Lycans will cower
from the very sight of it.

45:29.800 --> 45:32.371
- It's beautiful.
- Thomas knew that one day...

45:32.520 --> 45:34.761
...you would be beset
by enemies on both sides...

45:34.960 --> 45:36.007
...and he was right.

45:36.160 --> 45:39.528
David, this means that you are
the rightful heir of the Eastern Coven.

45:39.680 --> 45:42.490
Your mother and father
spent many months...

45:42.640 --> 45:44.802
...within the safety of these walls.

45:45.400 --> 45:46.811
Viktor grew suspicious.

45:46.960 --> 45:49.088
Then your father spirited you away...

45:49.240 --> 45:52.767
...before Semira arrived
with her troops.

45:54.200 --> 45:57.124
- And what of my mother?
- She returned to the Eastern Coven.

45:57.280 --> 45:58.486
The light in her eyes...

45:58.640 --> 46:01.530
Don't try and fabricate
some kind of martyrdom for her.

46:01.680 --> 46:03.456
I prefer a more honest
appraisal of her decision.

46:03.480 --> 46:06.927
She abandoned her only son
for the sake of her precious council.

46:07.080 --> 46:09.481
- Take it.
- David.

46:09.640 --> 46:11.244
David.

46:13.680 --> 46:15.967
Amelia asked me to give him this.

46:22.960 --> 46:24.962
[WIND WHISTLING]

46:33.960 --> 46:35.928
What do you need?

46:36.080 --> 46:37.889
Nothing. I just need to be left alone.

46:38.920 --> 46:40.604
Yes, I know the feeling.

46:41.360 --> 46:43.169
Why didn't my father
tell me about my mother?

46:43.640 --> 46:45.210
I did not know your father well...

46:45.400 --> 46:47.846
...but I know that his greatest fear
was to lose you.

46:48.000 --> 46:51.721
It seems it's the curse of every parent
to disappoint their child.

46:51.880 --> 46:55.202
- At least you fought for your child.
- Yes, and lost.

46:56.040 --> 46:58.850
You have pure-blood heritage, David.
Your mother was an Elder.

46:59.200 --> 47:01.487
Your parents kept you safe
for a reason.

47:01.640 --> 47:04.450
They protected you
so that one day you could lead.

47:06.600 --> 47:07.931
Your mother left you a gift.

47:11.440 --> 47:13.680
That's very kind of you,
but I have no use for jewellery.

47:13.800 --> 47:16.007
The ring is not the gift.

47:16.320 --> 47:18.891
It contains the gift: a mother's love.

47:20.080 --> 47:22.048
A single drop of her blood.

47:22.520 --> 47:24.409
Maybe it'll help you decide.

47:45.200 --> 47:47.806
[LENA CHANTING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

48:00.480 --> 48:02.164
LENA:
You're just in time.

48:02.680 --> 48:05.490
- Come.
- What is this?

48:05.640 --> 48:08.803
- Valissa, the in-between place.
- Is she dead?

48:08.960 --> 48:10.883
No.

48:11.960 --> 48:13.564
She is...

48:14.480 --> 48:15.481
...becoming.

48:15.680 --> 48:16.966
She took a poison.

48:17.160 --> 48:19.162
It allows her to visit the Sacred World.

48:19.560 --> 48:22.803
When she returns,
she will see this world with new eyes.

48:23.320 --> 48:24.810
I don't understand what this is.

48:25.000 --> 48:28.163
We have long known
there is more than just this world.

48:28.840 --> 48:31.047
When my father
first brought me down here...

48:31.200 --> 48:32.690
...I felt as you do now...

48:32.840 --> 48:36.845
...but I have since been
to the Sacred World many times.

48:38.080 --> 48:40.924
My eyes see beyond the surface
of so many things.

48:42.040 --> 48:44.611
- I see much about you.
- Such as?

48:44.760 --> 48:47.411
I can see you've loved a Lycan...

48:47.560 --> 48:49.528
...killed a vampire Elder
and given birth...

48:49.680 --> 48:50.681
Stop.

48:53.960 --> 48:57.407
I see you have lost your daughter...

48:57.560 --> 49:00.040
...and how much pain
this gives you deep inside...

49:00.200 --> 49:02.168
...where you will always hide it.

49:05.880 --> 49:07.245
She's a special child.

49:07.400 --> 49:09.687
Many battles will be fought...

49:10.480 --> 49:12.528
...and lost over her.

49:12.720 --> 49:14.802
- What else do you see?
- Darkness.

49:14.960 --> 49:16.724
One that touches us all.

49:17.120 --> 49:21.125
If you want to keep her safe,
you will need to go further...

49:21.280 --> 49:25.251
...than even a warrior of your renown
has ever ventured before.

49:25.440 --> 49:28.171
I have seen so much war...

49:28.360 --> 49:30.442
...so much killing.

49:30.600 --> 49:31.761
I cannot bear more.

49:31.920 --> 49:34.321
The peace you will feel here is real.

49:34.480 --> 49:37.927
It seeps into your skin
and comforts your soul.

49:38.120 --> 49:40.122
Tell me about the Sacred World.

49:40.760 --> 49:43.047
The water is the path.

49:48.960 --> 49:50.962
[♪♪♪]

50:00.440 --> 50:01.441
THOMAS:
<i>Amelia!</i>

50:01.640 --> 50:03.369
[ROARING]

50:04.480 --> 50:05.925
[YELLS THEN LYCAN GROWLS]

50:11.240 --> 50:13.846
AMELIA:
<i>I name our son David.</i>

50:14.000 --> 50:15.365
THOMAS:
<i>David.</i>

50:16.320 --> 50:18.561
AMELIA:
<i>One day, you will understand.</i>

50:18.720 --> 50:20.643
<i>I'm so sorry.</i>

50:20.800 --> 50:22.325
[CRYING]

50:24.080 --> 50:26.890
[PANTING]

50:28.480 --> 50:30.005
[♪♪♪]

50:33.160 --> 50:34.491
[LYCANS YELLING]

50:39.480 --> 50:40.970
DAVID:
Lycans! Sound the alarm!

50:41.120 --> 50:42.201
Close the doors!

50:42.920 --> 50:44.285
Move!

50:44.440 --> 50:45.521
[ALL CLAMOURING]

50:45.880 --> 50:48.724
[CLAMOURING IN DISTANCE]

50:50.920 --> 50:54.527
Just as I spoke of peace,
war has followed you here.

50:54.680 --> 50:55.886
Protect your own.

50:56.040 --> 50:57.769
I must find David.

51:06.000 --> 51:08.890
- We have to get you away.
- No. We led the Lycans here.

51:09.080 --> 51:11.401
We can't let these people die.

51:13.160 --> 51:15.162
[♪♪♪]

51:20.680 --> 51:22.091
[ALL MURMURING]

51:33.200 --> 51:35.202
[ALL SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

51:37.400 --> 51:39.402
[ALL YELLING THEN GUNFIRE]

51:48.320 --> 51:50.482
[SCREAMING]

51:56.800 --> 51:57.847
[SCREAMING]

52:04.880 --> 52:05.927
[YELLS]

52:06.080 --> 52:07.969
[BOTH GRUNTING]

52:09.080 --> 52:10.241
[GROANS]

52:11.560 --> 52:13.324
SELENE:
Run!

52:21.000 --> 52:22.081
LYCAN:
This way, men.

52:24.840 --> 52:26.968
Go around that side.

52:33.400 --> 52:35.050
[GROANING]

52:37.160 --> 52:38.491
[SCREAMING]

52:39.480 --> 52:42.324
[GRUNTS THEN GROWLING]

52:49.000 --> 52:50.445
[ROARS]

52:50.640 --> 52:51.846
[SHOUTING IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

52:52.280 --> 52:53.281
[YELLS]

52:54.640 --> 52:55.721
[GRUNTING]

53:02.400 --> 53:03.606
There she is.

53:04.080 --> 53:05.570
[LYCAN 1 SCREAMS]

53:06.520 --> 53:09.410
[GRUNTING]

53:24.960 --> 53:26.485
LYCAN 2:
You parasite.

53:26.680 --> 53:27.886
Just do it.

53:31.560 --> 53:33.369
[LYCAN ROARING
THEN LENA SHRIEKS]

53:34.840 --> 53:36.569
[GROANS]

53:46.000 --> 53:48.526
[GROWLING]

53:52.440 --> 53:54.442
[GRUNTING]

54:00.080 --> 54:02.401
[SNARLING]

54:03.440 --> 54:04.521
[ROARS]

54:08.560 --> 54:10.369
[YELLS]

54:13.720 --> 54:15.722
[ALL YELLING
AND SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

54:26.360 --> 54:27.361
Marius.

54:28.280 --> 54:29.645
At last.

54:30.440 --> 54:31.965
[GRUNTING]

54:33.200 --> 54:34.645
[BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY]

54:39.600 --> 54:40.601
[GRUNTING]

54:40.760 --> 54:41.841
[CHUCKLES]

54:43.040 --> 54:44.690
[YELLS THEN GROANS]

54:54.160 --> 54:56.083
- Aah!
LYCAN: On your right!

55:24.600 --> 55:26.602
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING
AND SCREAMING IN DISTANCE]

55:29.560 --> 55:31.085
I expected more from you.

55:49.680 --> 55:51.170
Tell me where your daughter is.

55:52.480 --> 55:54.528
I don't know.

55:54.920 --> 55:58.163
Selene, all I want is her blood.

56:09.800 --> 56:12.326
Only she can end this war.

56:13.080 --> 56:16.971
I give you my word
she will not be killed.

56:18.280 --> 56:19.850
[YELLS]

56:22.920 --> 56:24.126
[YELLS]

56:26.400 --> 56:27.731
[GROWLING]

56:34.600 --> 56:36.602
[GROWLING]

56:39.840 --> 56:41.444
[ROARS THEN GROWLING]

56:44.960 --> 56:45.961
What are you?

56:54.200 --> 56:55.645
[GRUNTING]

57:29.200 --> 57:31.328
[PANTS]

57:32.360 --> 57:33.521
[ROARS]

57:44.120 --> 57:45.360
[GROANING]

57:47.280 --> 57:48.930
[GROWLS]

57:53.600 --> 57:55.329
[GRUNTS THEN GASPS]

58:07.960 --> 58:11.521
Tell him where she is and all this
butchery will be over forever.

58:11.680 --> 58:13.762
I don't know.

58:13.920 --> 58:15.524
Lies.

58:22.840 --> 58:23.841
VIKTOR:
They've gone.

58:24.840 --> 58:26.365
SELENE:
<i>Michael.</i>

58:27.240 --> 58:30.210
EVE: I freed you.
THOMAS: <i>Look at the eyes.</i>

58:30.920 --> 58:32.604
EVE: <i>Who I am?
Do you not know who I am?</i>

58:32.760 --> 58:34.683
SELENE: <i>My daughter.</i>
EVE: <i>I don't want you.</i>

58:34.840 --> 58:36.604
<i>Don't look for me.</i>

58:37.800 --> 58:39.564
She's telling the truth.

58:41.800 --> 58:42.961
She doesn't know.

58:44.600 --> 58:46.045
[YELLS]

58:46.240 --> 58:47.765
[SELENE GRUNTS]

58:53.240 --> 58:55.641
My time is done.

58:56.880 --> 58:59.201
[ROARS]

58:59.360 --> 59:02.170
[HOWLING IN DISTANCE]

59:07.280 --> 59:08.691
[YELLS THEN GROWLS]

59:09.200 --> 59:11.441
They are retreating.

59:13.160 --> 59:15.162
[♪♪♪]

59:17.280 --> 59:19.123
I'm running out of time.

59:19.320 --> 59:21.641
We must strike against
the Eastern Coven now.

59:23.320 --> 59:24.924
You know what you must do.

59:35.880 --> 59:38.167
Water is the path.

59:51.840 --> 59:52.966
[GASPS]

01:00:10.440 --> 01:00:11.805
Selene.

01:00:12.000 --> 01:00:14.002
[♪♪♪]

01:00:19.400 --> 01:00:22.563
[CHANTING IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

01:00:25.800 --> 01:00:27.370
LENA:
<i>Praise the day...</i>

01:00:28.840 --> 01:00:30.604
<i>...when it ends.</i>

01:00:30.800 --> 01:00:33.280
<i>Praise the ice...</i>

01:00:33.480 --> 01:00:35.084
<i>...when it holds.</i>

01:00:35.880 --> 01:00:37.086
<i>Praise the sword...</i>

01:00:37.680 --> 01:00:39.728
<i>...when it kills.</i>

01:00:41.080 --> 01:00:42.684
<i>Praise the life...</i>

01:00:43.720 --> 01:00:45.563
<i>...that has lived.</i>

01:00:50.000 --> 01:00:52.002
[♪♪♪]

01:00:55.120 --> 01:00:56.963
It's time.

01:01:00.600 --> 01:01:02.011
Power.

01:01:02.160 --> 01:01:04.686
Such a seductively simple thing.

01:01:05.120 --> 01:01:08.283
Either you have it all
or you have nothing.

01:01:23.320 --> 01:01:24.765
[GOBLET SHATTERS]

01:01:24.920 --> 01:01:26.649
[LOW GROWLING]

01:01:31.400 --> 01:01:33.402
[GASPING]

01:01:45.600 --> 01:01:47.762
How fascinating.

01:01:51.320 --> 01:01:53.607
SELENE:
<i>Amelia...</i>

01:01:54.160 --> 01:01:57.721
<i>The water is the path.</i>

01:02:09.160 --> 01:02:11.128
You should stay here, David.

01:02:11.280 --> 01:02:13.487
This can be your home.

01:02:13.640 --> 01:02:15.085
Marius is heading east.

01:02:15.240 --> 01:02:16.765
There's nothing stopping him now.

01:02:17.400 --> 01:02:20.370
And my people are beset
with enemies on all sides.

01:02:20.600 --> 01:02:22.602
How can I stay here and live...

01:02:23.320 --> 01:02:26.324
- ...while they die?
- They need a leader.

01:02:26.480 --> 01:02:28.482
[♪♪♪]

01:02:41.280 --> 01:02:43.169
GUARD 1:
<i>Gate secure. Perimeter check.</i>

01:02:43.360 --> 01:02:44.725
[GATE BUZZES]

01:02:45.440 --> 01:02:46.930
ALEXIA:
Miss me?

01:02:47.080 --> 01:02:49.651
GUARD 2:  East gate is clear.
GUARD 3:  West gate clear.

01:02:50.400 --> 01:02:52.402
GUARD 4:
<i>Commencing perimeter sweep.</i>

01:02:54.120 --> 01:02:55.849
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Access granted.</i>

01:03:02.600 --> 01:03:04.204
What news do you bring?

01:03:04.360 --> 01:03:05.771
A massacre.

01:03:06.720 --> 01:03:09.291
The Lycans attacked
the fortress of Var Dohr.

01:03:09.440 --> 01:03:10.930
Lycans in the north.

01:03:13.240 --> 01:03:16.323
The Nordic Coven
was taken completely by surprise.

01:03:16.560 --> 01:03:20.246
- Dozens of vampires have been killed.
- Was Selene amongst them?

01:03:20.440 --> 01:03:23.808
Dead. Killed by Marius himself.

01:03:23.960 --> 01:03:26.406
Wherever Selene goes,
trouble surely follows.

01:03:26.560 --> 01:03:28.927
- What of David?
- I do not know.

01:03:29.080 --> 01:03:32.368
I only wished I had arrived sooner.
I might have helped in some way.

01:03:32.520 --> 01:03:35.205
Well, you've helped in so many ways.

01:03:35.360 --> 01:03:39.604
You've done exactly as I hoped
and planned, if not more.

01:03:40.800 --> 01:03:44.088
You see, information is power.

01:03:44.240 --> 01:03:46.607
[ALEXIA GASPING SOFTLY]

01:03:49.400 --> 01:03:53.041
And I collect it with a passion.

01:04:02.320 --> 01:04:05.369
Thank you for leading Marius
to the Nordic Coven.

01:04:05.520 --> 01:04:08.091
Your Lycan lover...

01:04:08.760 --> 01:04:11.570
...must be delighted
with his momentary success.

01:04:11.720 --> 01:04:13.085
[WEAPON STABS]

01:04:13.280 --> 01:04:15.282
You thought I didn't know.

01:04:15.440 --> 01:04:17.442
[ALEXIA GRUNTING AND GASPING]

01:04:18.120 --> 01:04:20.202
Foolish girl.

01:04:26.520 --> 01:04:28.522
[GURGLING]

01:04:28.760 --> 01:04:31.570
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Dawn alert. Sixty seconds to sunrise.</i>

01:04:35.880 --> 01:04:39.851
The Lycan scourge
destroyed an entire coven.

01:04:40.000 --> 01:04:42.128
To hide behind these walls
increases their advantage.

01:04:42.280 --> 01:04:44.169
We cannot take the war to Marius.

01:04:44.320 --> 01:04:46.527
Should we cower in the safety
of these walls...

01:04:46.680 --> 01:04:50.287
- ...while he picks us off one by one?
- Curb your insidious comments, Semira.

01:04:50.440 --> 01:04:52.966
This coven has held for 15 centuries.

01:04:53.120 --> 01:04:56.806
- It will hold for 15 more.
- I hoped you would show strength...

01:04:56.960 --> 01:05:00.567
...though I was willing
to settle for competence.

01:05:01.400 --> 01:05:03.004
[SEMIRA CLICKING TONGUE]

01:05:03.320 --> 01:05:04.526
I was wrong.

01:05:05.720 --> 01:05:07.006
[GUNS COCKING]

01:05:08.320 --> 01:05:10.288
What is the meaning of this?

01:05:10.440 --> 01:05:13.171
If this council is too weak
to take action...

01:05:13.320 --> 01:05:14.970
...it is my duty to do so.

01:05:15.120 --> 01:05:20.001
You are relieved of your duties as
council members effective immediately.

01:05:21.600 --> 01:05:23.250
[ALL MURMURING]

01:05:23.440 --> 01:05:25.488
The traitor returns.

01:05:27.400 --> 01:05:30.006
Oh, you are a fool
to show your face here.

01:05:30.760 --> 01:05:32.808
I will make you pay
for what you've done, Semira.

01:05:33.320 --> 01:05:35.400
Marius and his army
are heading this way as we speak.

01:05:36.240 --> 01:05:38.811
- I come to save my people.
- Your people? Heh.

01:05:38.960 --> 01:05:40.962
Kill him. Kill him.

01:05:41.160 --> 01:05:43.561
You aspire to be the protector
of your bloodline...

01:05:43.720 --> 01:05:46.200
...yet you kill your own kind
in pursuit of power.

01:05:46.360 --> 01:05:47.407
It ends now.

01:05:48.320 --> 01:05:51.642
I am David,
son of the great Elder Amelia.

01:05:52.520 --> 01:05:54.568
And I am the rightful heir to this coven.

01:05:54.760 --> 01:05:56.125
[LAUGHS]

01:05:56.400 --> 01:05:58.528
Amelia had no son.

01:06:00.000 --> 01:06:01.889
Well, she had the foresight...

01:06:02.040 --> 01:06:04.361
...to know that my claim
would be challenged.

01:06:05.960 --> 01:06:07.041
For the council.

01:06:07.200 --> 01:06:09.202
[♪♪♪]

01:06:23.280 --> 01:06:24.645
Amelia.

01:06:38.720 --> 01:06:40.449
His claim is true.

01:06:41.600 --> 01:06:44.888
David is the last of the purebloods.

01:06:46.640 --> 01:06:49.405
Irrelevant.
You are outnumbered and outgunned.

01:06:49.560 --> 01:06:51.722
Varga, your orders still remain.
Kill him.

01:06:55.960 --> 01:06:58.850
- I said, "Kill him."
- No.

01:07:02.960 --> 01:07:04.325
You swore to serve me.

01:07:04.480 --> 01:07:06.642
I swore to protect
the leader of this house.

01:07:07.160 --> 01:07:08.446
AUTOMATED VOICE:
<i>Breach detected.</i>

01:07:09.120 --> 01:07:11.282
<i>- Security system engaged.</i>
- Lycans. They're here.

01:07:11.440 --> 01:07:14.205
Lock her away until she can be judged
by the council.

01:07:14.360 --> 01:07:17.967
<i>Security system engaged.
Breach detected. Security system...</i>

01:07:18.120 --> 01:07:23.331
- She gets her damn war after all.
- Varga, you can still be forgiven.

01:07:23.480 --> 01:07:24.720
Gag her as well.

01:07:24.880 --> 01:07:27.281
[♪♪♪]

01:07:40.520 --> 01:07:41.806
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING]

01:07:53.200 --> 01:07:54.964
LYCAN:
Come on, move that truck. Move it.

01:07:55.120 --> 01:07:56.884
[INDISTINCT CHATTERING
CONTINUES]

01:08:01.880 --> 01:08:03.405
LYCAN:
Watch your angles!

01:08:05.320 --> 01:08:06.321
Let's go!

01:08:30.200 --> 01:08:31.326
Hold your positions.

01:08:37.319 --> 01:08:38.810
[THUMPING ON DOOR]

01:08:44.120 --> 01:08:45.645
[BEEPS]

01:08:54.080 --> 01:08:56.207
[LYCANS YELLING]

01:09:13.080 --> 01:09:15.731
LYCAN 1: On the staircase!
LYCAN 2: Behind you!

01:09:20.160 --> 01:09:22.731
- Fall back!
VAMPIRE: Retreat!

01:09:22.880 --> 01:09:24.881
[♪♪♪]

01:09:31.960 --> 01:09:34.281
[GROANING]

01:09:37.240 --> 01:09:38.399
DAVID:
Behind the balustrades!

01:09:38.800 --> 01:09:40.370
Take them out!

01:09:43.040 --> 01:09:45.691
[SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

01:09:53.160 --> 01:09:55.527
LYCAN 3: Come on!
LYCAN 4: Move, move, move!

01:09:57.360 --> 01:09:58.407
LYCAN 5:
Move it!

01:10:06.720 --> 01:10:08.324
Fuck.

01:10:09.960 --> 01:10:11.883
LYCAN 6:
Aim at the ready!

01:10:14.000 --> 01:10:15.525
Fire!

01:10:16.520 --> 01:10:18.010
[INAUDIBLE]

01:10:34.360 --> 01:10:36.362
[VAMPIRES SCREAMING]

01:10:39.360 --> 01:10:41.408
[♪♪♪]

01:10:42.560 --> 01:10:44.005
Fire!

01:10:47.000 --> 01:10:48.570
[VAMPIRES SCREAMING]

01:10:53.960 --> 01:10:55.405
[GROWLS]

01:11:00.000 --> 01:11:02.082
DAVID:
Hide from the light!

01:11:07.280 --> 01:11:09.169
VARGA:
Run!

01:11:09.320 --> 01:11:10.651
Move!

01:11:13.360 --> 01:11:14.480
LYCAN 7:
Shoot, shoot, shoot!

01:11:16.120 --> 01:11:18.122
[SCREAMING]

01:11:41.200 --> 01:11:43.009
[♪♪♪]

01:12:01.600 --> 01:12:03.011
[SCREAMING]

01:12:04.680 --> 01:12:06.045
[SCREAMING]

01:12:13.680 --> 01:12:15.284
[YELLING]

01:12:24.480 --> 01:12:26.687
[♪♪♪]

01:12:44.000 --> 01:12:45.570
Impossible.

01:12:45.720 --> 01:12:46.721
I saw you dead.

01:12:47.360 --> 01:12:48.361
I'm here.

01:12:48.520 --> 01:12:50.090
I brought backup.

01:12:50.240 --> 01:12:52.049
[ROARS]

01:12:53.920 --> 01:12:55.968
[ALL ROARING]

01:12:58.360 --> 01:12:59.441
There are too many of them.

01:13:01.480 --> 01:13:03.482
[ALL GROWLING]

01:13:08.680 --> 01:13:10.648
[LYCAN 1 HOWLING]

01:13:10.800 --> 01:13:12.325
[SNARLING]

01:13:13.480 --> 01:13:15.403
[ALL GRUNTING]

01:13:15.560 --> 01:13:17.369
[♪♪♪]

01:13:23.280 --> 01:13:24.327
[GROANS]

01:13:34.960 --> 01:13:36.166
[LYCAN 2 GROWLS]

01:13:36.960 --> 01:13:38.246
[YELLS]

01:13:52.520 --> 01:13:54.204
[GRUNTS]

01:14:22.600 --> 01:14:23.761
I've already killed you.

01:14:23.920 --> 01:14:25.684
[GRUNTING]

01:14:32.160 --> 01:14:33.366
Marius!

01:14:33.520 --> 01:14:34.726
[♪♪♪]

01:14:35.320 --> 01:14:37.243
[GRUNTING]

01:15:10.080 --> 01:15:12.481
[GRUNTS THEN GROANS]

01:15:36.520 --> 01:15:39.364
[♪♪♪]

01:15:42.440 --> 01:15:43.885
[SNARLING]

01:15:58.520 --> 01:15:59.760
[GROWLS]

01:16:13.920 --> 01:16:15.081
[GASPS]

01:16:15.640 --> 01:16:17.051
[GROWLS]

01:16:19.720 --> 01:16:21.210
Marius. Please.

01:16:24.720 --> 01:16:26.245
[GRUNTING]

01:16:26.440 --> 01:16:27.965
[MARIUS GROWLS]

01:16:34.720 --> 01:16:36.722
[♪♪♪]

01:16:38.640 --> 01:16:39.766
[GRUNTING]

01:16:51.560 --> 01:16:52.607
[♪♪♪]

01:17:05.320 --> 01:17:07.322
I wish your father
was alive to see this.

01:17:09.120 --> 01:17:11.282
His ridiculous dream
of you ruling this coven...

01:17:11.480 --> 01:17:13.289
...will be the very thing that kills you.

01:17:18.960 --> 01:17:20.485
Missed.

01:17:23.760 --> 01:17:25.762
[♪♪♪]

01:17:29.080 --> 01:17:31.811
Oh, it worked.

01:17:43.040 --> 01:17:44.041
[PANTING]

01:17:44.200 --> 01:17:45.281
[BEEPS]

01:18:01.120 --> 01:18:02.201
I'm one of you.

01:18:02.640 --> 01:18:04.563
No! No! No!

01:18:05.440 --> 01:18:07.920
[GROANING]

01:18:13.120 --> 01:18:15.043
[GASPS]

01:18:18.160 --> 01:18:19.730
You killed Michael.

01:18:23.680 --> 01:18:25.045
This is the last of him.

01:18:32.120 --> 01:18:34.122
[♪♪♪]

01:18:38.880 --> 01:18:40.484
[GASPS]

01:18:45.800 --> 01:18:47.609
[ROARING]

01:19:11.240 --> 01:19:13.481
DAVID: <i>You're family,
and you're all I have left.</i>

01:19:13.680 --> 01:19:14.841
EVE:
<i>Do you not know who I am?</i>

01:19:15.840 --> 01:19:17.126
[SNARLING]

01:19:20.560 --> 01:19:21.971
[MARIUS ROARING]

01:19:22.120 --> 01:19:23.884
[GRUNTING AND GASPS]

01:19:45.320 --> 01:19:48.130
[GROANS THEN SCREAMS]

01:19:50.000 --> 01:19:52.002
[GROWLING AND GASPING]

01:19:56.880 --> 01:19:58.962
[♪♪♪]

01:19:59.880 --> 01:20:01.245
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

01:20:06.280 --> 01:20:08.282
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING
IN DISTANCE]

01:20:17.640 --> 01:20:20.291
[ALL YELLING
AND SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

01:20:27.840 --> 01:20:29.126
Your leader is dead.

01:20:29.280 --> 01:20:30.884
[LYCANS GROWLING]

01:20:33.200 --> 01:20:35.168
Take your wounded. Leave.

01:20:35.320 --> 01:20:36.606
[GROWLS]

01:20:36.800 --> 01:20:38.290
Leave!

01:20:40.600 --> 01:20:43.444
[♪♪♪]

01:20:45.160 --> 01:20:48.289
ELENE: <i>We fought our greatest battle
in our darkest hour.</i>

01:20:49.280 --> 01:20:52.807
<i>After centuries of war
between vampire and Lycan...</i>

01:20:52.960 --> 01:20:55.930
<i>...this may at last be a time of peace.</i>

01:20:57.320 --> 01:20:59.800
<i>We must once again
tend to our wounded...</i>

01:21:00.000 --> 01:21:01.445
<i>...honour our fallen.</i>

01:21:01.600 --> 01:21:05.047
<i>Our final two covens
must find strength and unity...</i>

01:21:05.520 --> 01:21:08.000
<i>...to heal and rise from the ashes.</i>

01:21:14.680 --> 01:21:16.842
<i>My journey has now come full circle.</i>

01:21:17.000 --> 01:21:21.244
<i>Once an outcast, I am now
one of three chosen Elders.</i>

01:21:21.400 --> 01:21:23.607
<i>From hunted to the highest honour.</i>

01:21:33.360 --> 01:21:35.283
[♪♪♪]

01:21:49.240 --> 01:21:51.527
[WHISPERING]
<i>I have lived a thousand years.</i>

01:21:51.680 --> 01:21:54.126
<i>I may live a thousand more...</i>

01:21:54.280 --> 01:21:56.647
<i>...or I may die tomorrow.</i>

01:21:59.200 --> 01:22:01.441
<i>But I no longer fear death...</i>

01:22:01.640 --> 01:22:04.564
<i>...for I have known it once already.</i>

01:22:07.560 --> 01:22:09.005
[IN NORMAL VOICE]
<i>I am reborn...</i>

01:22:09.160 --> 01:22:12.004
<i>...and my eyes have been opened
to the Sacred World...</i>

01:22:12.160 --> 01:22:15.004
<i>...and to the promise
of what is yet to be.</i>

01:22:17.800 --> 01:22:19.848
<i>There is no beginning.</i>

01:22:20.240 --> 01:22:22.163
<i>There is no end.</i>

01:22:23.320 --> 01:22:25.687
<i>There is only becoming.</i>

01:22:28.920 --> 01:22:31.924
[♪♪♪]

